title: Jake Owen Judges Our ‘Thespian Throwdown’ + Lunchbox's Balloon Release Wishes + Happy 75th Birthday Dolly Parton!
itunes:title: Jake Owen Judges Our ‘Thespian Throwdown’ + Lunchbox's Balloon Release Wishes + Happy 75th Birthday Dolly Parton!
description:
Bobby talks with Jake Owen about his role in the new movie “Our Friend” and then sticks around to judge the guys in an acting competition. Today is Dolly Parton’s 75th Birthday! We celebrate by sharing stories you may not know about her and revisit some stories she told us when she stopped by the studio. Plus, Lunchbox was inspired by a news story so he wrote down five wishes and released them in a balloon in hopes that someone would find it and buy them for him!
